      "content": "im rly panicking and it's like 2am here so i cant get to a doctor right now anyway lol. its probably just a stomach bug or something. if i take a couple of extra ibuprofen and maybe some paracetamol it should help the pain so i can get some rest, right? i feel like i just need to ride it out until morning.",
